  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(It's been a few months since Futaro-kun went to Tokyo.\\n I'm working even harder as an actress now.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(I'm starting to feel the breadth of my work expanding\\n as I take on new types of roles.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(Beyond my dream of being an actress\\n is the place I'm aiming for.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro-kun, because you support me,\\n I can run towards that place.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Phew, I'm a little tired,\\nbut I have to work a little harder today.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Ah!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(It's from Futaro-kun. What could it be?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(Pfftt! What the hell is this emoji?\\n When would you use something like this?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(But it's great that Futaro-kun\\n has grown up enough to send \\n these kinds of emoji.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(I'll send one back as a response.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(...Oh? It was marked as read right away!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha!\\nMy goodness, that's just so typical.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " that didn't make sense earlier, right?]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": " I thought you'd check your phone\\n after you finished work.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hmm, I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " I'm on break now.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " I'm actually suuuper recharged by talking to you\\n during my break.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "good",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "[ｓ,3]that",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hmm? What am I waiting for?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "[ｓ,2]how",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "(What's this...\\n A selfie of Futaro-kun?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Pfftt, AHAHAHA!\\nWait, what is this?! What a weird pose!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Film Crew",
      "texto_en": "Nakano-saaan? What's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh, I'm sorry! Everything's fine!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " looked at me strangely.\\n How are you gonna fix this?]",
