      "texto_en": "Ahaha, he got flustered and made a typo.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": " a cool selfie of me just now.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " is that weird pose from earlier the coolest picture?]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": " Please delete it.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " I'll take a closer look when I get home.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Aha, he's so desperate.\\nCan't be helped.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hm, which one is good?\\nHow about this one?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
