      "texto_en": " I'll send you my favorite picture.]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " happy, right?\\n You secretly saved it, didn't you?]",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": " Your curiosity is obvious.]",
